  <title>JavaScript</title>
  </head>
  <body>
  <h1>JavaScript</h1>
  <p>JavaScript is a programming language commonly used to create interactive effects within web browsers.</p>
  <p><a href="EX-NO-02.html">Back to list</a></p>
  </body>
  </html>
